  "Financieel": "Financial",
  "For internal knowledge questions, document support, local chat flows, and API connections within your own environment, even when internet connections are unstable.": "For internal knowledge questions, document support, local chat flows, and API connections within your own environment, even when internet connections are unstable.",
  "For organizations that need just a bit more spec capacity or a specific offline workflow at hardware level.": "For organizations that need just a bit more spec capacity or a specific offline workflow at hardware level.",
  "For organizations that want to standardize prompt usage and help teams work faster with consistent output.": "For organizations that want to standardize prompt usage and help teams work faster with consistent output.",
  "For organizations with many content pages, knowledge articles, or documentation that must stay organized and easy to search.": "For organizations with many content pages, knowledge articles, or documentation that must stay organized and easy to search.",
  "For us, local AI was the deciding factor. AITJE is clear, works well inside our own network, and gives us more control over data and usage costs.": "For us, local AI was the deciding factor. AITJE is clear, works well inside our own network, and gives us more control over data and usage costs.",
