  "Huidige organisatie leren kennen": "Getting to know current organization",
  "If you only ask for a summary, you will get something general. Add your source text, purpose and desired style, and the result will be much better.": "If you only ask for a summary, you will get something general. Add your source text, purpose and desired style, and the result will be much better.",
  "Impact": "Impact",
  "Implementatie": "Implementation",
  "Implementation": "Implementation",
  "Important in practice": "Important in practice",
  "In 95% van de use-cases is dit al een efficiente oplossing. Onze out-of-the-box oplossing combineert een door ons ontwikkeld operating system, geoptimaliseerd voor de hardware, met een externe embedding-omgeving, een client-applicatie en lokale API-bereikbaarheid op het netwerk.": "In 95% of use cases, this is already an efficient solution. Our out-of-the-box solution combines an operating system developed by us, optimized for the hardware, with a remote embedding environment, a client application and local API accessibility on the network.",
  "In brief": "In letter",
  "In conversations about software development, backend is often about reliability, security and integrations. If you know what is meant by it, you can better evaluate projects and bids.": "In conversations about software development, backend is often about reliability, security and integrations. If you know what is meant by it, you can better evaluate projects and bids.",
  "Ja. Zolang er een internetverbinding beschikbaar is op het wifi- of lokale netwerk, kunnen AITJE-producten ook gebruikmaken van AI.": "Yes. As long as an internet connection is available on the Wi-Fi or local network, AITJE products can also use AI.",
  "In deze omgeving kunnen bestanden worden toegevoegd, geordend en verrijkt, zodat losse informatie verandert in een goed doorzoekbare en bruikbare kennisbasis. Daarmee wordt het eenvoudiger om content niet alleen op te slaan, maar ook logisch te structureren en later opnieuw in te zetten.": "In this environment, files can be added, organized and enriched, turning loose information into a searchable and usable knowledge base. This makes it easier not only to store content, but also to structure it logically and repurpose it later.",
  "In eigen beheer": "In house",
  "In gesprekken over softwareontwikkeling gaat backend vaak over betrouwbaarheid, veiligheid en integraties. Als je weet wat ermee bedoeld wordt, kun je projecten en offertes beter beoordelen.": "In conversations about software development, backend is often about reliability, security and integrations. If you know what is meant by it, you can better evaluate projects and bids.",
  "In gewone taal": "In plain language",
  "In het businessplan onderscheiden we drie persona’s: solo gebruikers, MKB en grotere organisaties. Elk pakket heeft de juiste mix van hardware, diensten en abonnementen voor die persona.": "In the business plan, we distinguish three personas: solo users, SMEs and larger organizations. Each package has the right mix of hardware, services and subscriptions for that persona.",
  "In het kenniscentrum schrijven we over termen en onderwerpen uit de wereld van AI. Misschien staat het antwoord op jouw vraag daar al tussen.": "In the knowledge center, we write about terms and topics from the world of AI. Perhaps the answer to your question is already among them.",
  "In het kort": "In brief",
  "In ons businessplan verwachten we dat Big Tech tarieven gaat verhogen zodra iedereen afhankelijk is. Met AITJE kies je voor vaste hardware + diensten op maat. Geen verrassingen.": "In our business plan, we expect Big Tech to start raising rates once everyone is dependent. With AITJE, you choose fixed hardware + customized services. No surprises.",
  "In ons kenniscentrum vind je artikelen over termen, technieken en toepassingen. Denk aan LLM's, RAG, context en lokale AI.": "In our knowledge center, you will find articles on terms, techniques and applications. Think LLMs, RAG, context and local AI.",
  "In plain language": "In plain language",
  "In short, AITJE Assistent OS is the link between the hardware, the AI functionality, and the devices around it: a stable and user-friendly foundation that keeps everything working together locally, in a controlled way, and smoothly.": "In short, AITJE Assistant OS is the link between the hardware, the AI functionality, and the devices around it: a stable and user-friendly foundation that keeps everything working together locally, in a controlled way, and smoothly.",
  "In short, the Knowledge Base is a smart link between source files and a usable digital knowledge environment, designed to give information more value, more context, and more coherence.": "In short, the Knowledge Base is a smart link between source files and a usable digital knowledge environment, designed to give information more value, more context, and more coherence.",
  "In this environment, files can be added, organized, and enriched so loose information becomes a searchable and usable knowledge base. That makes it easier not only to store content, but also to structure it logically and reuse it later.": "In this environment, files can be added, organized, and enriched so loose information becomes a searchable and usable knowledge base. That makes it easier not only to store content, but also to structure it logically and reuse it later.",
