  "Language model is the broad term. An LLM is a major language model within that category. In practice, by LLM, people usually mean modern models that support chats, summaries, classification and assistant tasks.": "Language model is the broad term. An LLM is a major language model within that category. In practice, by LLM, people usually mean modern models that support chats, summaries, classification and assistant tasks.",
