  "Less manual work, fewer errors and more predictability. But only if roles, exceptions and checkpoints are also properly accounted for in the design.": "Less manual work, fewer errors and more predictability. But only if roles, exceptions and checkpoints are also properly accounted for in the design.",
  "Let op": "Note",
  "LLM staat voor Large Language Model. Het is een taalmodel dat getraind is op grote hoeveelheden tekst en daardoor taal kan voorspellen, samenvatten, herschrijven en beantwoorden.": "LLM stands for Large Language Model. It is a language model that is trained on large amounts of text and therefore can predict, summarize, rewrite and respond to language.",
  "LLM stands for Large Language Model. It is a language model that is trained on large amounts of text and can therefore predict, summarize, rewrite and respond to language.": "LLM stands for Large Language Model. It is a language model that is trained on large amounts of text and can therefore predict, summarize, rewrite and respond to language.",
  "Local AI assistant on proprietary hardware with a knowledge base, offline access, and API connectivity.": "Local AI assistant on proprietary hardware with a knowledge base, offline access, and API connectivity.",
  "Local AI requires good hardware, management and clear choices about what stays local and what might run externally. It is not a trick, but an infrastructure choice with management burden and responsibility.": "Local AI requires good hardware, management and clear choices about what stays local and what might run externally. It is not a trick, but an infrastructure choice with management burden and responsibility.",
  "Local collaboration": "Local collaboration",
  "Lokaal waar het kan, extern waar het nodig is": "Local where possible, external where necessary",
  "Lokaal waar het kan, extern waar het nodig is. Extern doen we alleen op veilige plekken met betrouwbare partners en zonder afhankelijk te zijn van 1 service.": "Local where we can, external where we need to. External we do only in safe places with reliable partners and without depending on 1 service.",
  "Lokaal werken is daarnaast beter voor het milieu: minder eindeloze calls naar datacenters en efficienter gebruik van hardware. Gegevens blijven daarbij dichter bij de organisatie, in Europa en waar nodig volledig lokaal.": "Working locally is also better for the environment: fewer endless calls to data centers and more efficient use of hardware. Data stays closer to the organization, in Europe and, where necessary, completely local.",
  "Lokale agents en Raad van Bestuur": "Local agents and Board of Directors",
  "Lokale AI devices in meerdere vormen": "Local AI devices in multiple forms",
  "Lokale AI vraagt om goede hardware, beheer en duidelijke keuzes over wat lokaal blijft en wat eventueel nog extern draait. Het is geen trucje, maar een infrastructuurkeuze met beheerlast en verantwoordelijkheid.": "Local AI requires good hardware, management and clear choices about what stays local and what might run externally. It is not a trick, but an infrastructure choice with management burden and responsibility.",
