  "Terwijl prijzen van externe aanbieders kunnen stijgen, bouwen wij onze oplossingen zo dat kosten beheersbaar blijven en je minder afhankelijk bent van terugkerende platformkosten.": "While prices from external providers may rise, we build our solutions so that costs remain manageable and you are less dependent on recurring platform costs.",
  "That can be your question, earlier messages, documents, instructions, roles, examples, or company information. Anything that helps the model answer more specifically is context.": "That can be your question, earlier messages, documents, instructions, roles, examples, or company information. Anything that helps the model answer more specifically is context.",
  "The AITJE team built a smart solution for my driving school. After every lesson, students automatically get a clear summary of their progress and points for improvement.": "The AITJE team built a smart solution for my driving school. After every lesson, students automatically get a clear summary of their progress and points for improvement.",
  "The backend is the layer behind an app or website. It is where requests are processed, permissions are checked, data is retrieved, and business logic is executed.": "The backend is the layer behind an app or website. It is where requests are processed, permissions are checked, data is retrieved, and business logic is executed.",
  "The backend is the part of software where logic, data processing and links run out of the user's view.": "The backend is the part of software where logic, data processing and links run out of the user's view.",
  "The chat uses selected content as a knowledge base and gives answers in natural language, including summaries and references.": "The chat uses selected content as a knowledge base and gives answers in natural language, including summaries and references.",
  "The client makes AITJE accessible on multiple devices at once while everything stays local, clear, and controlled. That combines ease of use with control over access and infrastructure.": "The client makes AITJE accessible on multiple devices at once while everything stays local, clear, and controlled. That combines ease of use with control over access and infrastructure.",
  "The combination of recording conversations, summarizing them, and getting the information back in a structured way works very well here.": "The combination of recording conversations, summarizing them, and getting the information back in a structured way works very well here.",
  "The context window is the maximum amount of information a model can carry at once in a single interaction.": "The context window is the maximum amount of information a model can carry at once in a single interaction.",
  "The front end is the part of software that users see and work with directly.": "The front end is the part of software that users see and work with directly.",
  "The frontend displays information and collects input. The backend processes that input, retrieves data and returns results. Together, they form the user experience and the technical operation behind it.": "The frontend displays information and collects input. The backend processes that input, retrieves data and returns results. Together, they form the user experience and the technical operation behind it.",
  "The frontend is the interface of a website, dashboard or app. There, a user sees screens, forms, buttons, notifications and navigation.": "The frontend is the interface of a website, dashboard or app. There, a user sees screens, forms, buttons, notifications and navigation.",
  "The Knowledge Base helps organizations process documents and knowledge intelligently, organize them logically, and turn them into a searchable and usable knowledge foundation.": "The Knowledge Base helps organizations process documents and knowledge intelligently, organize them logically, and turn them into a searchable and usable knowledge foundation.",
  "The more autonomy you give, the more important it becomes to get permissions, logging, data access and checkpoints right. An agent must fit within your governance.": "The more autonomy you give, the more important it becomes to get permissions, logging, data access and checkpoints right. An agent must fit within your governance.",
  "The software creates links between documents and their components, provides insight into structure, priority, and coherence, and makes it possible to export and synchronize knowledge in a controlled way.": "The software creates links between documents and their components, provides insight into structure, priority, and coherence, and makes it possible to export and synchronize knowledge in a controlled way.",
  "The software offers management capabilities for settings, devices, knowledge sources, and support, so the full environment remains not only accessible but also practically manageable.": "The software offers management capabilities for settings, devices, knowledge sources, and support, so the full environment remains not only accessible but also practically manageable.",
  "Think of servers, APIs, databases, authentication, logs, and integrations with other systems. Users usually do not see these components directly, but they determine how the software works.": "Think of servers, APIs, databases, authentication, logs, and integrations with other systems. Users usually do not see these components directly, but they determine how the software works.",
  "This creates an environment in which information can be managed better, found faster, and shared more easily. Teams gain more overview and can work with fewer loose documents.": "This creates an environment in which information can be managed better, found faster, and shared more easily. Teams gain more overview and can work with fewer loose documents.",
  "This is not a religious choice. Some processes are fine in the cloud, while others need to remain local for reasons of continuity, security or control. It's all about finding the right balance per situation.": "This is not a religious choice. Some processes are fine in the cloud, while others need to remain local for reasons of continuity, security or control. It's all about finding the right balance per situation.",
  "This solution makes WordPress content easier to find and more useful with AI-powered search functionality and contextual answers.": "This solution makes WordPress content easier to find and more useful with AI-powered search functionality and contextual answers.",
  "Through an API, an app can, for example, retrieve customer data, send documents, invoke an AI model or write information back to another system. It is thus the connection layer between different tools and processes.": "Through an API, an app can, for example, retrieve customer data, send documents, invoke an AI model or write information back to another system. It is thus the connection layer between different tools and processes.",
  "Through the local API, users can ask questions, share documents, and work with the assistant from different devices without relying on an external cloud environment.": "Through the local API, users can ask questions, share documents, and work with the assistant from different devices without relying on an external cloud environment.",
  "Thuiszorg vult rapportage via voice agent": "Home care fills reporting via voice agent",
