  "Wie AI gebruikt via externe platformen, deelt vaak ongemerkt documenten, vragen, interne kennis en bedrijfscontext met partijen buiten de eigen organisatie. Veel bedrijven staan daar nog te weinig bij stil.": "Those who use AI through external platforms often unknowingly share documents, questions, internal knowledge and business context with parties outside their own organization. Many companies are still too little aware of this.",
  "Wie AI volledig bouwt op externe platformen, bouwt ook mee aan een afhankelijkheid van prijswijzigingen, voorwaarden en keuzes van grote buitenlandse partijen.": "Those who build AI entirely on external platforms are also building in dependence on price changes, terms and choices from large foreign parties.",
  "Wie nu bewust keuzes maakt in infrastructuur en data, voorkomt later dure migraties, lock-in en afhankelijkheid van platformen die hun prijsmodel veranderen.": "Those who make conscious choices in infrastructure and data now avoid costly migrations, lock-in and dependence on platforms that change their pricing models later.",
  "Winkelcoordinator": "Store coordinator",
  "With an API, you usually actively request information. A webhook works the other way around: a system reports by itself that something new has happened. Often you use them together in the same integration.": "With an API, you usually actively request information. A webhook works the other way around: a system reports by itself that something new has happened. Often you use them together in the same integration.",
  "With edge AI, you process data close to the source: on a device, server or network in your own environment. That's why edge AI is often called local AI.": "With edge AI, you process data close to the source: on a device, server or network in your own environment. That's why edge AI is often called local AI.",
  "With good APIs, you can connect systems without rebuilding everything from scratch. That makes automation, integration and scalability a lot more practical, provided permissions, logging and error handling are properly managed.": "With good APIs, you can connect systems without rebuilding everything from scratch. That makes automation, integration and scalability a lot more practical, provided permissions, logging and error handling are properly managed.",
  "With the RAG chat and the book-entry app, we find the right metadata faster and staff can locate niche books much more easily.": "With the RAG chat and the book-entry app, we find the right metadata faster and staff can locate niche books much more easily.",
  "With this software you manage the API, define access, and determine which devices may connect to the hardware that runs AITJE. That creates one central place from which communication, access, and collaboration between different devices are managed.": "With this software you manage the API, define access, and determine which devices may connect to the hardware that runs AITJE. That creates one central place from which communication, access, and collaboration between different devices are managed.",
  "Within the local network, AITJE Assistent OS allows other devices to communicate easily with the hardware. Think of laptops, tablets, or other systems using the same smart assistant, data, or functionality over LAN.": "Within the local network, AITJE Assistant OS allows other devices to communicate easily with the hardware. Think of laptops, tablets, or other systems using the same smart assistant, data, or functionality over LAN.",
